text: Nicole Eggert (born January 13, 1972) is an American actress. She played Jamie Powell in the television series Charles in Charge. She played Summer Quinn in Baywatch. Eggert was born in Glendale, California. ==References== == Other websites == * Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from Glendale, California Category:1972 births Category:Living people
